>The Minister for Women has overall responsibility for policy on gender equality.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-02-17T16:28:52Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Women)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-for-women","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women","content_id":"c0e08038-d200-42ce-8c8d-ac17f9e2bd3b","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-09-17T17:26:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Women)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state-minister-for-equalities","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state-minister-for-equalities","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-of-state-minister-for-equalities","content_id":"871a9d80-d9ec-4219-bccb-28afa271bd9e","details":{"body":"<ul>\n  <li>Racial and ethnic disparities</li>\n  <li>Inclusive Britain Strategy</li>\n  <li>Inclusion at Work Panel oversight</li>\n  <li>Equality Act and Public Sector Equality Duty oversight</li>\n  <li>Sponsoring minister for the Social Mobility Commission and the Equality and Human Rights Commission</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-06-16T12:07:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister of State (Minister for Equalities)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state-minister-for-equalities","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities","content_id":"ccea3444-4897-431d-b77e-a202a4d3a85c","details":{"body":"<p>The Minister for Equalities’ responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Equality for LGBT people in the UK (at home, work, health and wellbeing)</li>\n  <li>Banning conversion therapy in England and Wales</li>\n  <li>LGBT equality in the workplace</li>\n  <li>LGBT safety (including homelessness and domestic violence)</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-04-28T08:05:38Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary-minister-for-women","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary-minister-for-women","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary-minister-for-women","content_id":"6a85445d-5f2a-41d1-a97f-a3e61aee78b7","details":{"body":"<p>Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>supporting the Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster on equalities</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-10-11T14:08:33Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister for Women","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary-minister-for-women","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-equalities","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-equalities","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-for-equalities","content_id":"1ea11e47-c72b-42e3-b31d-d77405123051","details":{"body":"<p>Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>equalities including oversight of the Government Equalities Office</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":37,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-10-19T13:55:16Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister for Equalities","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-for-equalities","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary--8","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary--8","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary--8","content_id":"7dfd35f4-3418-4976-8f97-c1e4ebff8cd6","details":{"body":"<p>Responsibilities include supporting the Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster in matters relating to equalities, including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Equality Hub business in the House of Lords</li>\n  <li>Race Disparity Unit and race and ethnicity policy</li>\n  <li>LGBT policy</li>\n  <li>social mobility and regional inequality</li>\n  <li>Equality and Human Rights Commission</li>\n  <li>Social Mobility Commission</li>\n  <li>equalities legislative framework</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-10-14T11:50:22Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Secretary (Minister for Equalities)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-secretary--8","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities--2","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities--2","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities--2","content_id":"6aad2f64-4fa4-4f39-807c-b92989936d94","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-10-28T10:27:24Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-equalities--2","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women--2","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women--2","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women--2","content_id":"cc66be59-c4b7-44cc-be0f-e5cc2e64918d","details":{"body":"<p>The Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Women) is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>driving women’s policy and the government’s wider priorities for women and girls, including tackling violence against women and girls (with the Minister for Safeguarding)</li>\n  <li>tackling maternal and mental health disparities for minority groups</li>\n  <li>supporting improvements to the provision and accessibility of childcare to support working parents</li>\n  <li>progressing the Worker Protection Bill through Parliament</li>\n  <li>delivery of the government’s Inclusive Britain Action Plan</li>\n  <li>sponsorship of the Equality and Human Rights Commission</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-02-28T12:10:16Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Women)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-women--2","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--221","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--221","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--221","content_id":"3d82e71d-7ddb-4545-951c-60c826e5535d","details":{"body":"<p>The Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities) is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>advancing the government’s wider priorities for LGBT equality, including:\n    <ul>\n      <li>improving LGBT safety</li>\n      <li>supporting LGBT people fleeing persecution</li>\n      <li>tackling LGBT homelessness</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>preparing and progressing the Conversion Practices Bill through pre-legislative scrutiny and then through Parliament</li>\n  <li>progressing regulations to enable opposite-sex couples to convert their marriage to a civil partnership</li>\n  <li>sponsorship of the Social Mobility Commission, supporting work on geographic and socio-economic disparities</li>\n  <li>overview of the overarching equalities legislative framework, including the Equality Act</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-02-28T12:38:38Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--221","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"ed53d23f-63aa-45bc-8111-0040a73014cb","details":{"body":"<p>Policy Fellow to the Minister for Women and Equalities in the Equality Hub.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"special_representative_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-03-15T15:30:02Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Policy Fellow to the Minister for Women and Equalities","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state-disabled-people","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state-disabled-people","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-of-state-disabled-people","content_id":"61e0d9bf-9325-44dc-85ba-a71a4603c4d6","details":{"body":"<p>Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>disability policy and cross-government responsibility for disabled people</li>\n  <li>oversight of Disability Unit, and convenor of Disability Champions</li>\n  <li>work and health strategy, including sponsorship of the joint Department for Work and Pensions / Department for Health and Social Care Work and Health Unit, and disability benefit reform</li>\n  <li>disability employment, and disability employment programmes</li>\n  <li>financial support for those at risk of falling out of work, and disabled claimants including, Disability Living Allowance (<abbr title=\"Disability Living Allowance\">DLA</abbr>), Personal Independence Payment (<abbr title=\"Personal Independence Payment\">PIP</abbr>), Employment and Support Allowance (<abbr title=\"Employment and Support Allowance\">ESA</abbr>) and Carer’s Allowance (<abbr title=\"Carer's Allowance\">CA</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>Support for disadvantaged groups</li>\n  <li>Youth Offer</li>\n  <li>Government Equalities Office (<abbr title=\"Government Equalities Office\">GEO</abbr>) lead, Women and the Menopause</li>\n  <li>Military Covenant</li>\n  <li>Housing Benefit strategy and delivery, including Support for Mortgage Interest and supported accommodation</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>Between December 2023 and April 2024 this role was carried out by the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-disabled-people-health-and-work\">Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Minister for Disabled People, Health and Work)</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-26T09:00:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister of State (Minister for Disabled People, Health and Work)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state-disabled-people","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_successor_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1426","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-equality-and-opportunity","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-equality-and-opportunity","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-equality-and-opportunity","content_id":"398859b6-695e-42dd-ad68-826f06db871d","details":{"acronym":"OEO","brand":"cabinet-office","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Office for Equality<br/>and Opportunity"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Office for Equality and Opportunity","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-equality-and-opportunity","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1324","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/the-equality-hub","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/the-equality-hub","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-equality-hub","content_id":"0f8a33d1-f7fa-4f7a-a1d0-8e3424ab01b2","details":{"acronym":"","brand":"cabinet-office","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5fdb2d75d3bf7f40